Simulated percentile ranks 
\begin_inset Formula $(\check{s}_{it},\check{s}_{2t})$
\end_inset

 from model (
\begin_inset LatexCommand \ref{chi1}

\end_inset

).
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset LatexCommand \label{fig1}

