\end_inset

 The distribution of the 
\begin_inset Formula $\check{s}_{t}$
\end_inset

 is compared to the distribution of the 
\begin_inset Formula $\check{y}_{t}$
\end_inset

.
 Good estimates of 
\begin_inset Formula $\theta$
\end_inset

 and 
