\begin_inset Formula $s_{t}$
\end_inset

 and calculating the corresponding 
\begin_inset Formula $\check{s}_{t}$
\end_inset

.
 An appropriate choice for 
\begin_inset Formula $\theta$
\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset Formula $\rho$
\end_inset

 is indicated by a low value of chi--squared goodness of fit statistic 
\begin_inset Formula \begin{equation}
X^{2}\equiv\sum_{c}\frac{(o_{c}-e_{c})^{2}}{e_{c}}\ ,\label{chisq}\end{equation}

\end_inset

 where the 
\begin_inset Formula $c$
\end_inset

 sum extends over all cells.
 In practice 
\begin_inset Formula $X^{2}$
\end_inset

