 Since 
\begin_inset Formula \[
P(U_{2}>u|U_{1}>u)=\frac{P(U_{2}>u,U_{1}>u)}{P(U_{1}>u)}=\frac{P(U_{1}>u|U_{2}>u)P(U_{2}>u)}{P(U_{1}>u)}=P(U_{1}>u|U_{2}>u)\ ,\]

\end_inset

 it makes no further sense to ask the question the other way round.
